snippet.title: TV MADness | MAD Parody Video List | Cartoon Network
snippet.description: They say imitation is the sincerest form of flattery. If that's true, then MAD must love TV, because they've mashed up, spoofed and skewered every show worth watching. Let the MADness begin!

snippet.title: Talking Fish
snippet.description: After trying to find candy inside it, Flapjack has a talk with the fish he caught. Watch more Flapjack on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: No Talking
snippet.description: Bugs tries to get Lola to stop talking so they can enjoy their date. Watch more of The Looney Tunes Show on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Tiger Talk
snippet.description: Watch more Uncle Grandpa on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Water Cooler Talk!
snippet.description: Watch more MAD on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: K'nuckles Catches a Fish
snippet.description: Flapjack tries to explain to K'nuckles that the fish they caught is real, not candy. Watch More Flapjack on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Pep Talk
snippet.description: Finn is distraught after a very un-heroic run-in with some evil gnomes. Fortunately, his good buddy Jake is there to give him a heroic pep talk! Watch more Adventure Time on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Talking to Ladies
snippet.description: Jake pretends to be a chick snail to show Snorlock how to talk to a lady. Watch more Adventure Time on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: A Serious Talk
snippet.description: Pops orders Benson to stop yelling at Mordecai and Rigby. Watch more Regular Show on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Cactus Kaiser
snippet.description: Lyle tries to talk the Cactus Kaiser into returning to the game. Watch more Level Up on Cartoon Network!
